DIE Springbok-groep vir die Britse en Ierse Leeus-reeks is Saterdagaand bekendgemaak. Rosko Specman, Joseph Dweba, Aphelele Fassi, Wandisile Simelane, Sanele Nohamba en Yaw Penxe is van die nuwelinge in die groep. Die veteraan-losskakel Morne Steyn, wat met sy 52m strafskop die reeks in 2009 teen die Leeus beklink het, is ook ingesluit. Duane Vermeulen, wat Vrydag die veld met 'n besering verlaat het, is ook deel van die groep terwyl spelers soos Marcell Coezee en Cornal Hendricks hulself ongelukkig kan ag. So lyk die span: Stutte:Thomas du Toit (Sharks)Steven Kitshoff (Stormers)Vincent Koch (Saracens)Frans Malherbe (Stormers)Ox Nché (Sharks)Trevor Nyakane (Vodacom Bulls)Coenie Oosthuizen (Sale Sharks) Hakers:Joseph Dweba (Bordeaux-Bègles)Malcolm Marx (Kubota Spears)Bongi Mbonambi (Stormers)Scarra Ntubeni (Stormers) Slotte:Lood de Jager (Sale Sharks)Eben Etzebeth (Toulon)Nicolaas Janse van Rensburg (Montpellier)Franco Mostert (Honda Heat)Marvin Orie (Stormers)RG Snyman (Munster) Losvoorspelers:Dan du Preez (Sale Sharks)Pieter-Steph du Toit (Stormers)Siya Kolisi (Sharks)Kwagga Smith (Yamaha Júbilo)Marco van Staden (Vodacom Bulls)Duane Vermeulen (Vodacom Bulls)Jasper Wiese (Leicester Tigers) Veelsydige voorspelers:Jean-Luc du Preez (Sale Sharks)Rynhardt Elstadt (Toulouse) Skrumskakels:Faf de Klerk (Sale Sharks)Herschel Jantjies (Stormers)Sanele Nohamba (Sharks)Cobus Reinach (Montpellier)Losskakels:Elton Jantjies (Pau)Handré Pollard (Montpellier)Morné Steyn (Vodacom Bulls)Senters:Lukhanyo Am (Sharks)Damian de Allende (Munster)Jesse Kriel (Canon Eagles)Wandisile Simelane (Emirates Lions)Frans Steyn (Toyota Cheetahs)Buite-agterspelers:Aphelele Fassi (Sharks)Cheslin Kolbe (Toulouse)Willie le Roux (Toyota Verblitz)Makazole Mapimpi (Sharks)Sbu Nkosi (Sharks)Yaw Penxe (Sharks)Rosko Specman (Toyota Cheetahs)Damian Willemse (Stormers)